title: Democrats nominate first black woman for governor
text:
Democrats nominate first black woman for governor 9:20am EDT - 01:42
Democratic voters rallied on Tuesday for the chance to make history in November by selecting a ticket filled with female candidates, including a bid to elect the first African-American female governor in the United States. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
